    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-09-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-09-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="360"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d360">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hunter</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-09-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 13, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 191.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                    dispatch, No. 245, of the 21st ultimo, reporting the arrival of the United
                    States cruiser <hi rend="italic">Newark</hi> at San José, Guatemala, and the
                    courtesies shown to Capt. C. F. Goodrich and his officers on their visit to
                    Guatemala City.</p>
                <p>At the instance of the Acting Secretary of the Navy, to whom Captain Goodrich has
                    reported the matter, you will express to President Cabrera the thanks of the
                    Navy Department for the generous hospitality extended to Captain Goodrich and
                    his officers.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
